{
  "message": "Rename python-conventions to following-conventions\n\nEstablish a consistent naming pattern for language plugins (e.g.,\npython:following-conventions, rust:following-conventions, etc). This\navoids redundancy in the skill name and makes the convention applicable\nacross different language ecosystems.\n\nBump version to 0.4.0 for this breaking change.",
